line_1: Amongst his well known pheers attempts to mell:
line_2: That shall ere long his matchless swiftness quell;

line_1: Amongst his well known pheers attempts to mell:
line_2: With horn and hoof his purpose they repell.

line_1: Amongst his well known pheers attempts to mell:
line_2: Your sex, my Daphne, show their vengeance sell;

line_1: Wi' bitter, dearthfu' wines to mell,
line_2: Ye Scots wha wish auld Scotland well,

line_1: Wi' bitter, dearthfu' wines to mell,
line_2: Ye chief, to you my tale I tell,

line_1: Wi' bitter, dearthfu' wines to mell,
But ay keep mind to moop an' mell,
line_2: Wi' sheep o' credit like thysel!

line_1: As Heaven and Earth they would together mell:
line_2: Soft-tinkling Streams, and dashing Waters fell,

line_1: As Heaven and Earth they would together mell:
line_2: (So work'd the Wizard) wintry Storms to swell,

line_1: As Heaven and Earth they would together mell:
line_2: The Demons of the Tempest, growling fell,
